=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> EnabledBrowserExtensions => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

Specify the browser extensions allowed for your Amazon Q web
experience.

=over

=item *

C<CHROME> E<mdash> Enables the extension for Chromium-based browsers
(Google Chrome, Microsoft Edge, Opera, etc.).

=item *

C<FIREFOX> E<mdash> Enables the extension for Mozilla Firefox.

=item *

C<CHROME> and C<FIREFOX> E<mdash> Enable the extension for
Chromium-based browsers and Mozilla Firefox.

